{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.008.066,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. 2 Ch 7:11-22. (Ge 17:1-8. De 29:22-28.) (Mt 24:2.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Lorsque Salomon eut achev\u00e9 de b\u00e2tir la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, la maison du roi, et tout ce qu\u2019il lui plut de faire,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.2","name":"1 Rois 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.8.66","name":"1 Rois 8:66","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.8.66"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>l\u2019\u00c9ternel apparut \u00e0 Salomon une seconde fois, comme il lui \u00e9tait apparu \u00e0 Gabaon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.3","name":"1 Rois 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.1","name":"1 Rois 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel lui dit: J\u2019exauce ta pri\u00e8re et ta supplication que tu m\u2019as adress\u00e9es, je sanctifie cette maison que tu as b\u00e2tie pour y mettre \u00e0 jamais mon nom, et j\u2019aurai toujours l\u00e0 mes yeux et mon c\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.4","name":"1 Rois 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.2","name":"1 Rois 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et toi, si tu marches en ma pr\u00e9sence comme a march\u00e9 David, ton p\u00e8re, avec sinc\u00e9rit\u00e9 de c\u0153ur et avec droiture, faisant tout ce que je t\u2019ai command\u00e9, si tu observes mes lois et mes ordonnances,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.5","name":"1 Rois 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.3","name":"1 Rois 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>j\u2019\u00e9tablirai pour toujours le tr\u00f4ne de ton royaume en Isra\u00ebl, comme je l\u2019ai d\u00e9clar\u00e9 \u00e0 David, ton p\u00e8re, en disant: Tu ne manqueras jamais d\u2019un successeur sur le tr\u00f4ne d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.6","name":"1 Rois 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.4","name":"1 Rois 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mais si vous vous d\u00e9tournez de moi, vous et vos fils, si vous n\u2019observez pas mes commandements, mes lois que je vous ai prescrites, et si vous allez servir d\u2019autres dieux et vous prosterner devant eux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.7","name":"1 Rois 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.5","name":"1 Rois 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>j\u2019exterminerai Isra\u00ebl du pays que je lui ai donn\u00e9, je rejetterai loin de moi la maison que j\u2019ai consacr\u00e9e \u00e0 mon nom, et Isra\u00ebl sera un sujet de sarcasme et de raillerie parmi tous les peuples.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.8","name":"1 Rois 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.6","name":"1 Rois 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et si haut plac\u00e9e qu\u2019ait \u00e9t\u00e9 cette maison, quiconque passera pr\u00e8s d\u2019elle sera dans l\u2019\u00e9tonnement et sifflera. On dira: Pourquoi l\u2019\u00c9ternel a-t-il ainsi trait\u00e9 ce pays et cette maison?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.9","name":"1 Rois 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.7","name":"1 Rois 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et l\u2019on r\u00e9pondra: Parce qu\u2019ils ont abandonn\u00e9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, leur Dieu, qui a fait sortir leurs p\u00e8res du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, parce qu\u2019ils se sont attach\u00e9s \u00e0 d\u2019autres dieux, se sont prostern\u00e9s devant eux et les ont servis; voil\u00e0 pourquoi l\u2019\u00c9ternel a fait venir sur eux tous ces maux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.10","name":"1 Rois 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.8","name":"1 Rois 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Villes b\u00e2ties par Salomon. Navires envoy\u00e9s \u00e0 Ophir<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-28: cf. 2 Ch 8. Ec 2:2-10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>\n    Au bout de vingt ans, Salomon avait b\u00e2ti les deux maisons, la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et la maison du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.11","name":"1 Rois 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.9","name":"1 Rois 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Alors, comme Hiram, roi de Tyr, avait fourni \u00e0 Salomon des bois de c\u00e8dre et des bois de cypr\u00e8s, et de l\u2019or, autant qu\u2019il en voulut, le roi Salomon donna \u00e0 Hiram vingt villes dans le pays de Galil\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.12","name":"1 Rois 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.10","name":"1 Rois 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Hiram sortit de Tyr, pour voir les villes que lui donnait Salomon. Mais elles ne lui plurent point,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.13","name":"1 Rois 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.11","name":"1 Rois 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>et il dit: Quelles villes m\u2019as-tu donn\u00e9es l\u00e0, mon fr\u00e8re? Et il les appela pays de Cabul, nom qu\u2019elles ont conserv\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.14","name":"1 Rois 9:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.12","name":"1 Rois 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Hiram avait envoy\u00e9 au roi cent vingt talents d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.15","name":"1 Rois 9:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.13","name":"1 Rois 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Voici ce qui concerne les hommes de corv\u00e9e que leva le roi Salomon pour b\u00e2tir la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et sa propre maison, Millo, et le mur de J\u00e9rusalem, Hatsor, Meguiddo et Gu\u00e9zer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.16","name":"1 Rois 9:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.14","name":"1 Rois 9:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Pharaon, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte, \u00e9tait venu s\u2019emparer de Gu\u00e9zer, l\u2019avait incendi\u00e9e, et avait tu\u00e9 les Canan\u00e9ens qui habitaient dans la ville. Puis il l\u2019avait donn\u00e9e pour dot \u00e0 sa fille, femme de Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.17","name":"1 Rois 9:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.15","name":"1 Rois 9:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et Salomon b\u00e2tit Gu\u00e9zer, Beth-Horon la basse,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.18","name":"1 Rois 9:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.16","name":"1 Rois 9:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Baalath, et Thadmor, au d\u00e9sert dans le pays,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.19","name":"1 Rois 9:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.17","name":"1 Rois 9:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>toutes les villes servant de magasins et lui appartenant, les villes pour les chars, les villes pour la cavalerie, et tout ce qu\u2019il plut \u00e0 Salomon de b\u00e2tir \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, au Liban, et dans tout le pays dont il \u00e9tait le souverain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.20","name":"1 Rois 9:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.18","name":"1 Rois 9:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Tout le peuple qui \u00e9tait rest\u00e9 des Amor\u00e9ens, des H\u00e9thiens, des Ph\u00e9r\u00e9ziens, des H\u00e9viens et des J\u00e9busiens, ne faisant point partie des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.21","name":"1 Rois 9:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.19","name":"1 Rois 9:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>leurs descendants qui \u00e9taient rest\u00e9s apr\u00e8s eux dans le pays et que les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl n\u2019avaient pu d\u00e9vouer par interdit, Salomon les leva comme esclaves de corv\u00e9e, ce qu\u2019ils ont \u00e9t\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.22","name":"1 Rois 9:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.20","name":"1 Rois 9:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mais Salomon n\u2019employa point comme esclaves les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; car ils \u00e9taient des hommes de guerre, ses serviteurs, ses chefs, ses officiers, les commandants de ses chars et de sa cavalerie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.23","name":"1 Rois 9:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.21","name":"1 Rois 9:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Les chefs pr\u00e9pos\u00e9s par Salomon sur les travaux \u00e9taient au nombre de cinq cent cinquante, charg\u00e9s de surveiller les ouvriers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.24","name":"1 Rois 9:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.22","name":"1 Rois 9:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>La fille de Pharaon monta de la cit\u00e9 de David dans sa maison que Salomon lui avait construite. Ce fut alors qu\u2019il b\u00e2tit Millo.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.25","name":"1 Rois 9:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.23","name":"1 Rois 9:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Salomon offrit trois fois dans l\u2019ann\u00e9e des holocaustes et des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces sur l\u2019autel qu\u2019il avait b\u00e2ti \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il br\u00fbla des parfums sur celui qui \u00e9tait devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Et il acheva la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.26","name":"1 Rois 9:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.24","name":"1 Rois 9:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le roi Salomon construisit des navires \u00e0 \u00c9tsjon-Gu\u00e9ber, pr\u00e8s d\u2019\u00c9loth, sur les bords de la mer Rouge, dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9dom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.27","name":"1 Rois 9:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.25","name":"1 Rois 9:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Et Hiram envoya sur ces navires, aupr\u00e8s des serviteurs de Salomon, ses propres serviteurs, des matelots connaissant la mer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.28","name":"1 Rois 9:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.26","name":"1 Rois 9:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 9:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.009.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.010.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.9.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Ils all\u00e8rent \u00e0 Ophir, et ils y prirent de l\u2019or, quatre cent vingt talents, qu\u2019ils apport\u00e8rent au roi Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9","name":"1 Rois 9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.1","name":"1 Rois 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.10.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.27","name":"1 Rois 9:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.9.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb29c51d0.49245754');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb29c51d0.49245754\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb29c51d0.49245754","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb29c51d0.49245754'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb29c51d0.49245754\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}